            "title": "滬指開市跌2點 深成指跌21點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以3226點開市，跌2點或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報10142點，亦跌21點或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌5點或0.14%，開報3789點；創業板指數開市報2059點，跌3點或0.17%。</p>\n</div>",
