        {
            "title": "傳京東再研收購德國電子產品零售商Ceconomy",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《彭博》引述消息人士報道，指京東(09618)重新研究收購德國電子產品零售商Ceconomy的可行性。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Ceconomy官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/Ceconomy-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Ceconomy官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/Ceconomy-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Ceconomy官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Ceconomy是歐洲電子產品零售領域的重要企業，在歐洲大陸經營約1000家門市。報道指出，若京東成功收購Ceconomy，除了可擴大京東規模外，集團的物流部門配送網絡，亦可與對方的實體店形成互補。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道又指出，京東近期已就潛在交易與Ceconomy初步接洽，並開始試探對方主要股東的意向。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">早在2023年底，京東已曾對Ceconomy表達興趣。踏入2025年以來，Ceconomy股價穩步向上，市值已約達15億歐元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14685816-%e5%82%b3%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1%e5%86%8d%e7%a0%94%e6%94%b6%e8%b3%bc%e5%be%b7%e5%9c%8b%e9%9b%bb%e5%ad%90%e7%94%a2%e5%93%81%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e5%95%86ceconomy",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241112_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 09:10:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "綠景中國遭提清盤呈請  渉21萬美元財務義務",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綠景中國(00095)公布，獲悉翹石集團環球於2025年2月4日向香港高等法貸款另加應計利息財務義務。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"綠景中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/LGEM_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"綠景中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/LGEM_WEB_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">綠景中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">高等法院已將呈請的首次聆訊日期定為2025年4月9日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公布稱，公司極力反對呈請，將徵詢法律意見，並採取一切必要行動保護其合法權利。董事會認為呈請並沒有依據、不代表公司 其他利益相關者之利益，及可能損害本公司的價值。董事會認為呈請並不會對公 司商業營運及財務狀況帶來重大不利影響。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14685815-%e7%b6%a0%e6%99%af%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%81%ad%e6%8f%90%e6%b8%85%e7%9b%a4%e5%91%88%e8%ab%8b-%e6%b8%8921%e8%90%ac%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e8%b2%a1%e5%8b%99%e7%be%a9%e5%8b%99",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/LGEM_WEB_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 09:05:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "智雲健康通過接入DeepSeek提升智雲大腦",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">智雲健康(09955)發自願公告，披露該公司已通過接入DeepSeek提升智雲大腦。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250205_FI_source-ap_DeepSeek.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250205_FI_source-ap_DeepSeek.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司表示，將DeepSeek-R1模型接入其專屬醫療AI智雲大腦，進一步增強智雲大腦的數據挖掘能力，並提升公司醫院SaaS及藥店SaaS的慢病管理效率。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14685794-%e6%99%ba%e9%9b%b2%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e9%80%9a%e9%81%8e%e6%8e%a5%e5%85%a5deepseek%e6%8f%90%e5%8d%87%e6%99%ba%e9%9b%b2%e5%a4%a7%e8%85%a6",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/09955-web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-06 08:50:24",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        }
    ]
